      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Adult Social Care Infection Control Fund: round 2
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Sets out the infection control measures that the new infection control fund will support, including information on the distribution of funds and reporting requirements.</p>

  </div>
</div>

